    // AboutUs Page
    "aboutUs.hero.about": "About",
    "aboutUs.hero.swamGroup": "SWAM Group",
    "aboutUs.hero.description":
      "Leading the industry since 1978 as the country's largest manufacturer of Rotary Blowers, Compressors and Vacuum Pumps & allied systems",
    "aboutUs.stats.globalInstallations": "Global Installations",
    "aboutUs.stats.exportCountries": "Export Countries",
    "aboutUs.stats.capacity": "m³/hr Capacity",
    "aboutUs.companyStory.paragraph1":
      "Founded in 1978 by the visionary and innovation-driven Chairman and Managing Director, Mr. S.K. Gambhir, SWAM Group has established itself at the forefront in the engineering and manufacturing domain. A scholar at heart, Mr. Gambhir's holds a B.Tech degree from one of India's supremely reputed institutes and a postgraduate degree in business administration, the foundation to his six decades of unmatched leadership. Over the years, his contributions to esteemed institutions such as Engineers India Limited, which is well-regarded for its project management and consultancy within the Oil and gas sector.",
    "aboutUs.companyStory.paragraph2":
      "SWAM was built with Mr. Gambhir's bold vision: to engineer solutions that power industries across the world. In the past four decades, the organization has skyrocketed to be ranked among India's largest",
    "aboutUs.companyStory.paragraph3":
      "manufacturers of Rotary, Compressors, Blowers, Vacuum Pumps and allied systems. With a market expanse across the nation and international markets, SWAM has transformed into a future-focused industrial powerhouse managed via state-of-the-art facilities. The next-generation technology infusion at SWAM is visible in the form of advanced tools and operational processes, all directed to better cater to customer needs.",
    "aboutUs.companyStory.paragraph4":
      "We are committed to upholding the legacy of engineering precision and innovation at the core. The product category at SWAM, particularly rotary blowers with capacities of up to 100,000 m³/hr, are the result of decades of research, development, and hands-on experience. Each of our manufacturing facilities has an in-house testing facility that can accommodate up to 1000KW with 6.6KV testing arrangements. This ensures every product item meets the highest global quality grades and safety standards before it is sent to the market.",
    "aboutUs.companyStory.paragraph5":
      "We take pride in our 55000+ installations worldwide that have successfully powered vital infrastructure and industrial processes. Our brand name resonates well in the global markets, with our products exported to 25+ countries. Apart from India, SWAM also has dedicated offices in Australia and a strong presence of workforce in the United States and UAE. Such a global footprint helps us stay well-knit with customers and deliver localized support at the earliest.",
    "aboutUs.companyStory.paragraph6":
      "The leadership at SWAM believes in bringing the right balance among machines and solutions that are capable of empowering industries at large. From petrochemicals, energy, pharmaceuticals, food processing to wastewater treatment, our systems are aligned to bring in better performance, scalability and sustainability.",
    "aboutUs.companyStory.paragraph7":
      "SWAM is a brand that is well rooted in its values and origin which breathes- passion, excellence, and customer-first ideology. We are moving forward to deliver engineering solutions that have the power to reshape tomorrow with new-age possibilities.",
    "aboutUs.features.advancedTechnology.title": "Advanced Technology",
    "aboutUs.features.advancedTechnology.description":
      "Next-generation solutions with cutting-edge equipment",
    "aboutUs.features.continuousGrowth.title": "Continuous Growth",
